hat can make poisons above 100 skill. So I'm taking the bull by the horns to be the one. Granted, i know it's not profitable at all (how many rogues do you know that use poisons?) but I would feel great knowing I supplied Bazzer, Fathferd or the just about planes ready Storgue with a mysterious resin that could do a measly 250+ damage in a single hit. Call me deranged or whatever, but I'll be using my special blends when I feel the urge. <br>
<br>
Yes, The craft is quite expensive, but I have this uncanny whim to be completely broke and have a bank full of deadly toxins. like I said, call me deranged....<br>
<br>
Anyhow, I'll be checking out the raid signups, seeing who is next on the hitlist. if I may be able to concoct a mixture to help, I will do so. It may not be much, but I'll feel as if i helped, at least in the smallest way. <br>
<br>
Guild rogues - if there is a raid you are going on, and you would like to use a special toxin, let me know, I'll do my best. I do not need the exact one you need, just a vauge implication....  <br>
      ex: I'm doing this undead guy in Kith, have anything that could help?<br>
      res: sure, I can make a nasty undead only toxin that would do...hmmm, you're level 55, right?...about 300 or so of extra damage to that measly 25+ of your dagger. I'll make you a few..<br>
<br>
just trying to start a bit of interest in my wares. I figure if there's even the smallest interest in it, that will encourage me even more....<br>
<br>
that's enought rambling....<br>
<br>
to sum it up = Guild rouge who would like a dose of poison for their blades, give me a yell<br>
<br>
Thankies,<br>
